                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><encodingDesc><tagsDecl>&amp;renditions;</tagsDecl></encodingDesc></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_īwzærdyg" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>īwzærdyg</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>ewzærdug</orth></form><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>преданный</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>faithful</q></tr></sense><etym xml:lang="ru">Из %iīw-zærd-yg%i буквально „единосердечный“; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/> <w>yakdil</w> <gloss><q>единодушный</q></gloss></mentioned> (%iуаk%i ‘один’, %idil%i ‘сердце’), <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>ertguli</w> <gloss><q>преданный</q></gloss></mentioned> из %ierti%i ‘один’ и %iguli%i ‘сердце’. Ср. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_dyzærdyg"/>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It is from %iīw-zærd-yg%i, literally it means „of one heart“; cf. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/> <w>yakdil</w> <gloss><q>of one mind</q></gloss></mentioned> (%iуаk%i ‘one’, %idil%i ‘heart’), <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>ertguli</w> <gloss><q>faithful</q></gloss></mentioned> from %ierti%i ‘one’ and %iguli%i ‘hearth’. Cf. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_dyzærdyg"/>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>